{
  "stem": "3848.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the both of them went in, they ate a little bit, and they felt a little better.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He tells me, you are going with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Now we are going to sign into the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we won't-- I won't let you go now that I found you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I see you going with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I said to him, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I can't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I have a job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They have 40 people working on top there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I am the machinist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "If I don't show up, 40 people won't be working.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He says, I can't let you go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I can't let you stay here anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You're going to have to go with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Well, I decided to go with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I left the job without informing anybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We-- from there on, I slept on the station again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The next morning there was a transport going to Guzar, near the Afghanistan border where the Polish army was assembling.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we traveled all the way through the desert, practically, to go to this place of Guzar.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "When we-- when I left my job, I had a friend that was working there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "The next morning he came to see me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He was the only one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "His name was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Schtekl. ?] He came to tell me that the work wasn't going on all night, that somebody took over the machine to work on it, and they overloaded it, and they burned the-- the-- the engine, the motor that was working, electric motor that was working for this purpose.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And they're looking for me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Well, you can imagine how I felt.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
